  <name>Sitra</name>
  <summary>Get fonts from online sources</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Get your fonts from online sources with a sleek, friendly user interface.
      Sitra provides a seamless experience for installing, uninstalling and previewing fonts.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>List fonts available on Google Fonts</li>
      <li>Preview the fonts using Fontsource CDN for privacy</li>
      <li>Get code to use the font in your project, via CDN or npm from fontsource</li>
      <li>Download the fonts on your device in ttf format from google</li>
      <li>Filter font by category using the toggle buttons or by family and subset using search</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <developer id="io.github.ronniedroid">
    <name>Ronnie Nissan</name>
  </developer>

